Class DoFnAdapters

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.beam.sdk.transforms.DoFnAdapters
  • Deprecated. 
    This class will go away when we start running DoFn's directly (using DoFnInvoker) rather than via OldDoFn.

public class DoFnAdapters
extends Object
